      <div>
      <% include ../near.css %>
      
      <p class='csiro-near-p'>
      CSIRO Energise survey participants were asked a number of questions about the type and usage of heating appliances, and their level of comfort with and without heating.
      </p>
      
      <h4 class='csiro-near-h4'>Type of Heating Appliance</h4>
      <p class='csiro-near-p'>
      What type(s) of heating does your household have? (select all that apply)</p>
      
       <ul class='csiro-near-ul'>
        <li><strong>Type - Wood/Coal: </strong> Wood or coal fire</li>
        <li><strong>Type - Ducted: </strong> Gas or electric central heating</li>
        <li><strong>Type - Under Floor: </strong> Gas or electric under floor heating</li>
        <li><strong>Type - Air Conditioner: </strong> Air conditioning unit(s) that are used as heater(s)</li>
        <li><strong>Type - Other: </strong> Other type(s) of heating</li>
        <li><strong>Type - None: </strong> N/A – do not have any heating</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h4 class='csiro-near-h4'>Heating in the past week</h4>
      <p class='csiro-near-p'>
      Thinking about the past seven days, how many days did your household use at least one heater or heating system? </p>
      <p class='csiro-near-p'>
      Contextual help: If your household did not use any heating in the past seven days, please answer ‘0’. </p>
      <ul class='csiro-near-ul'>
        <li><strong>Usage - 0 Days: </strong> Not used</li>
        <li><strong>Usage - 1-2 Days: </strong> 1-2 Days</li>
        <li><strong>Usage - 3-4 Days: </strong> 3-4 Days </li>
        <li><strong>Usage - 5-6 Days: </strong> 4-5 Days </li>
        <li><strong>Usage - 7 Days: </strong> Every day </li>
      </ul>
      
