      <p class='csiro-near-p'>
      Thinking about the past seven days, how did you feel at home when the heating was on?</p>
      <ul class='csiro-near-ul'>
        <li><strong>Comfort with Heating - Much Colder: </strong> A lot colder than I would have liked</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort with Heating - Slightly Colder: </strong> A little colder than I would have liked</li>
